review_text: Its a really small park, so its get crowded easily!

(Translated by Google) I stopped at this park to eat a take out of McDoonald's. A few benches and 2 picnic tables. Homeless people occupied several places but I did not feel threatened. I did it quickly.

(Original)
J'ai arrêté à ce parc pour manger un take out de McDoonald's. Quelques bancs et 2 tables à pique nique.  Des itinérants occupaient plusieurs places mais je ne me suis pas sentie menacée.  J'ai fait ça vite.
